  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the effects of aroma massage to sleep quality of the nurses and
      staff during night shift.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Night shift increases physical and psychological pressure, and even affects their sleep
      quality. This study aims to evaluate the effects of aroma massage to sleep quality of the
      nurses during night shift after life-style modification and/or aroma massage. The
      investigators adopt a Randomized Controlled Trial (RCT) in this study. The investigators
      expect aroma massage would improve the sleep quality during night shift.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
